<SYNC Start=1233797><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1235501><P Class=KRCC>
켄신
<SYNC Start=1236468><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1237269><P Class=KRCC>
그럼 켄신, 잘 가!
<SYNC Start=1238896><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1243075><P Class=KRCC>
