<SYNC Start=1258321><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1258858><P Class=KRCC>
나보다 잘하잖아
<SYNC Start=1260519><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1260593><P Class=KRCC>
