<SYNC Start=1263084><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1263162><P Class=KRCC>
괜찮아! 그러면 이렇게!
<SYNC Start=1266723><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1266799><P Class=KRCC>
어, 어라~
<SYNC Start=1269597><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1269668><P Class=KRCC>
