<SYNC Start=1272159><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1272705><P Class=KRCC>
굉장한 힘이오
<SYNC Start=1276038><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1278711><P Class=KRCC>
가만히 좀 있게나
<SYNC Start=1280508><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1280579><P Class=KRCC>
