Ah gimme your love
<SYNC Start=1358145><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1358223><P Class=KRCC>
요염하게 lady<br>
I need your love
<SYNC Start=1362216><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1362294><P Class=KRCC>
가끔씩 보이는<br>
