<SYNC Start=1366628><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1366699><P Class=KRCC>
무엇을 말하는지<br>
모르겠어
<SYNC Start=1370533><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1370602><P Class=KRCC>
솔직하게 lady<br>
Ah gimme your love
<SYNC Start=1374561><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1374640><P Class=KRCC>
느껴봐 날 lady<br>
I need your love
<SYNC Start=1378667><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1378744><P Class=KRCC>
너의 몸짓에 빠져들어
<SYNC Start=1382908><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1382982><P Class=KRCC>
